ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I do not recommend it unless you want to study health economics.
A great course for learning about latest research in public finance.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was good and very helpful that Amanda focused us on developing ideas that we can actually use for research.
The course provided a great overview of recent research in public finance and encouraged us to come up with serious ideas for research.

This course not only provides me more insights about public finance and taxation policy, but also gets me familiar with potential mathematical models or statistical analysis that can be implemented into my research.
